<li class="toclevel-3 tocsection-37"><a href="#.E3.83.89.E3.82.A2.E3.82.92.E9.96.8B.E3.81.91.E3.81.9F.E3.82.8A.E9.96.89.E3.82.81.E3.81.9F.E3.82.8A.E3.81.99.E3.82.8B.E3.81.AB.E3.81.AF.3F"><span class="tocnumber">4.2.6</span> <span class="toctext">ドアを開けたり閉めたりするには?</span></a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-38"><a href="#Minecraft.E3.83.97.E3.83.AC.E3.83.BC.E3.83.A4.E3.83.BC.E5.90.91.E3.81.91"><span class="tocnumber">4.3</span> <span class="toctext">Minecraftプレーヤー向け</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-3 tocsection-39"><a href="#.E4.BD.9C.E6.A5.AD.E5.8F.B0.E3.81.AF.E3.81.82.E3.82.8A.E3.81.BE.E3.81.99.E3.81.8B.3F"><span class="tocnumber">4.3.1</span> <span class="toctext">作業台はありますか?</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-3 tocsection-40"><a href="#Minetest.2FMinetest_Game.E3.81.A8Minecraft.E3.81.AE.E9.81.95.E3.81.84.E3.81.AF.3F"><span class="tocnumber">4.3.2</span> <span class="toctext">Minetest/Minetest GameとMinecraftの違いは?</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-3 tocsection-41"><a href="#Minetest_Game.E3.82.92Minecraft.E3.81.AE.E3.82.88.E3.81.86.E3.81.AB.E3.81.99.E3.82.8B.E3.81.AB.E3.81.AF.E3.81.A9.E3.81.86.E3.81.97.E3.81.9F.E3.82.89.E3.81.84.E3.81.84.E3.81.A7.E3.81.99.E3.81.8B.3F"><span class="tocnumber">4.3.3</span> <span class="toctext">Minetest GameをMinecraftのようにするにはどうしたらいいですか?</span></a></li>
